<scene name="opening">
	<shot>
		<image src="com.bored.games.darts.assets.story.Scene01" />
		<dialogue>
			<line frame="com.bored.games.darts.assets.BalloonYellow" actor="Narrator" x="400" y="48">Not far from Manchester lies a small pub built atop the blitz-ruins of an experimental dart manufacturing-plant...</line>
		</dialogue>
	</shot>
	<shot>
		<image src="com.bored.games.darts.assets.story.Scene02" />
		<dialogue>
			<line frame="com.bored.games.darts.assets.BalloonTailLeft" actor="Hero" x="146" y="73">Whew! Sure is cozy being in here away from this awful weather with such beautiful company.</line>
			<line frame="com.bored.games.darts.assets.BalloonTailRight" actor="Heroine" x="222" y="97">You fancy the bartender? I'm not sure he's listening.</line>
		</dialogue>
	</shot>
	<shot>
		<image src="com.bored.games.darts.assets.story.Scene03" />
		<dialogue>
			<line frame="com.bored.games.darts.assets.BalloonNarrowTailSide" actor="Rogue's Gallery" x="330" y="195">Do I hear some kaylied Yank chattin' up my dishy lil sis? His napper's rank to come in here!</line>
		</dialogue>
	</shot>
	<shot>
		<image src="com.bored.games.darts.assets.story.Scene04" />
		<dialogue>
			<line frame="com.bored.games.darts.assets.BalloonNarrowTailSide" actor="Big Bill" x="229" y="12">You'd better be the dog's bollocks with the arrows if you're to get pissed in our pub!</line>
			<line frame="com.bored.games.darts.assets.BalloonNarrowTailTop" actor="Hero" x="381" y="249">You want me to do what to a dog?</line>
			<line frame="com.bored.games.darts.assets.BalloonNarrowTailLong" actor="Old Man" x="-83" y="309">Crikey! Don't get gutted just yet.</line>
		</dialogue>
	</shot>
	<shot>
		<image src="com.bored.games.darts.assets.story.Scene05" />
		<dialogue>
			<line frame="com.bored.games.darts.assets.BalloonTailInsideLeft" actor="Old Guy" x="192" y="34">House rules say that anyone can stay as long as they play darts, and Bob's your uncle!</line>
		</dialogue>
	</shot>
</scene>